'''掌水工'''，是[[嘉南大圳|嘉南]][[農田水利會|農田水利會]]為加強其轄境內[[灌溉|灌溉]]用[[水資源|水資源]]管理而實施的一種制度<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.economic-news.tw/2017/01/Save-Water-Irrigation.html|title=「掌水工」立大功 節約9,300萬噸灌溉用水|last=經濟部|first=|date=|work=|newspaper=經新聞|accessdate=2017-03-06|language=zh-TW|archive-date=2017-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170306212142/http://www.economic-news.tw/2017/01/Save-Water-Irrigation.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該制度之產生背景為當地[[水庫|水庫]]淤積難以改善以及氣候異常導致之水資源匱乏<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://udn.com/news/story/7326/1868821|title=掌水工薪資高達2.5億 嘉南農田水利會爭補助不成|last=周宗禎|first=|date=2016-08-02|work=|newspaper=聯合新聞網|accessdate=2017-03-06|archive-date=2017-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170306210629/https://udn.com/news/story/7326/1868821|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該制度之執行者多為當地[[農民|農民]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.daai.tv/daai-web/news/topic_content.php?id=949655&cls=811|title=掌水工看管用水 節約水大功臣|accessdate=2017-03-06|author=朱怡蓉 蕭宏澍|date=|work=www.daai.tv|publisher=大愛電視 DaAi TV|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170306212214/http://www.daai.tv/daai-web/news/topic_content.php?id=949655&cls=811|archivedate=2017年3月6日|df=}}</ref>，其任務為灌溉責任區的灌溉用水調配、巡查水路<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://udn.com/news/story/11034/2407448|title=1300名「掌水工」調度用水 年省1水庫水源|author=謝進盛|last=|date=2017-04-17|work=|newspaper=聯合報|accessdate=2017-06-14|archive-date=2019-02-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190228064512/https://udn.com/news/story/11034/2407448|dead-url=no}}</ref>，以及維修責任區之給水路<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/local/paper/648655|title=〈南部〉《小檔案》掌水工|accessdate=2017-03-06|author=楊金城|date=|work=m.ltn.com.tw|publisher=自由時報電子報|archive-date=2017-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170306211053/http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/local/paper/648655|dead-url=no}}</ref>。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/local/paper/648654|title=〈南部〉《供灌幕後功臣》阿公掌水工 使命必達|author=|date=|work=自由時報電子報|accessdate=2017-06-14}}</ref>

